data.text:
Just hours after joking about the royal baby, Jimmy Fallon became a father himself.

The Late Night host and his wife, producer Nancy Juvonen, welcomed a baby girl on Tuesday, a spokesperson for the couple confirmed to The Hollywood Reporter.The new parents are “overjoyed about the arrival of their beautiful daughter,” the spokesperson added.
